526
00:34:10,381 --> 00:34:11,841
Yo no sospeché de él.

527
00:34:11,924 --> 00:34:12,759
Yo tampoco.

528
00:34:13,551 --> 00:34:15,261
Yo sí. Tiene razón.

529
00:34:16,012 --> 00:34:18,139
